## 3. Our Solution

We are building an **AI-powered financial companion** that meets young adults where they are — with zero assumptions about prior knowledge. Finance Buddy combines four core pillars into one app:

| Pillar | What It Does |
|--------|-------------|
| **Learn** | Adaptive financial education with AI-generated lessons, a course library of 20+ topics, XP/level gamification, and plain-language explanations of every concept from compound interest to ETFs. |
| **Budget** | AI-powered budget tracking with expense categorization, spending insights, recurring expense management, savings goals with progress tracking, and personalized recommendations to optimize spending. |
| **Invest (Simulated)** | Paper trading portfolio with simulated live market data, stock education, risk level explanations, Roth IRA and 401K management tools, and AI-explained recommendations — all with zero real money at risk. |
| **Ask** | An always-available AI chatbot companion (named by the user) that answers personal finance questions, analyzes the user's budget and portfolio, and provides contextual guidance in plain language. |

**Key differentiators:**
- The AI companion is **named by the user** and referenced throughout the entire app, creating a personal relationship with financial learning
- Every recommendation includes an **educational explanation** — the app teaches as it guides
- The user **always controls every decision** — the AI advises, it never acts unilaterally
- **Paper trading mode** lets users practice investing with zero risk before using real money
- All AI responses include **both opportunities and risks** — no blind optimism

