### AI Integration

All AI features are powered by the **Anthropic Claude API** (`claude-sonnet-4-20250514`). The backend acts as a trusted proxy — the frontend never holds an API key. AI is used for:

- **Onboarding profile generation** — warm, personalized financial profile summaries
- **Budget insights** — analyzing spending patterns and suggesting improvements
- **Stock explanations** — explaining companies and market concepts in plain language
- **Chat companion** — streaming conversational AI with full user context
- **Insight cards** — personalized recommendations with educational explanations
- **Recommendation rationale** — every suggestion includes the "why" and associated risks

Chat responses use **Server-Sent Events (SSE)** for real-time streaming, giving users an interactive conversational experience.

### Future ML Architecture (Phase 4)

The long-term vision includes a custom **machine learning recommendation engine** trained on historical market data. This will use:

- **Data sources**: ~3-5 million rows of price history, technical indicators, fundamentals, and macroeconomic data (~4-7 GB total)
- **Model candidates**: LSTM for time-series prediction, XGBoost/LightGBM for buy/hold/sell classification, Transformer architectures for long-range pattern capture, and ensemble methods combining all approaches
- **Training timeline**: 3-6+ months of research, data acquisition, and training
- **Important caveat**: AI stock prediction has well-documented limitations (detailed in Section 8) — the app is transparent about these

