## 7. Legal & Compliance Awareness

We are transparent about the regulatory landscape:

- The app provides **educational guidance and decision support only** — not financial advice
- All recommendations are framed as learning opportunities with both opportunities and risks presented
- A persistent disclaimer will be displayed: *"This is an educational simulator. Not financial advice. No real money is involved. Paper trading only."*
- Users must be **16 years or older** to create an account
- Full Terms of Service and Privacy Policy are planned for production release
- We acknowledge that personalized stock recommendations could trigger SEC/FINRA scrutiny — legal counsel will be consulted before any public release
- The double-confirmation process for trade recommendations protects users from impulsive decisions

